# Copy to `apps/api/.dev.vars` to override values during local `wrangler dev`.
# `.dev.vars` is git-ignored.

# Optional: only needed if you want the live cloud-tile proxy at
# /api/weather/clouds/... Get a free key at https://openweathermap.org/api.
# OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=

# Optional: comma-separated list of allowed CORS hostnames. Each entry matches
# the exact host plus any subdomain. Use `*` for any origin.
# ALLOWED_ORIGINS=*
